      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-nns-sto-025.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    =    "I"
                     go to acc-nns-sto-999.
           if        w-tes-rns-sto (1)    =    01
                     go to acc-nns-sto-050
           else      go to acc-nns-sto-999.
       acc-nns-sto-050.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
