      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      v-num                to   w-tes-nns-sto (1)      .
       acc-nns-sto-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-nns-sto-425.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se non si e' in inserimento si ripristina   *
      *                  * il valore salvato, lo si rivisualizza, e    *
      *                  * si esce                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    =    "I"
                     go to acc-nns-sto-450.
           move      w-sav-nns-sto        to   w-tes-nns-sto (1)      .
           perform   vis-nns-sto-000      thru vis-nns-sto-999        .
           go to     acc-nns-sto-800.
       acc-nns-sto-450.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
